Urshifu (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0891: Kubfu
Pokémon
#0893: Zarude →

Urshifu has been featured on 8 different cards since it debuted in the Battle Styles expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Urshifu cards are typically Fighting-type Stage 1 Pokémon, and may be Water-type or Darkness-type depending on the form depicted.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Urshifu

Urshifu
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
